summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting from the State of Washington a Correction Quit Claim Deed conveying to the City of Seattle portions of the west one-half of Section 32, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and portions of the east one-half of Section 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and laying off 1st Avenue South, Occidental Avenue South, South Cloverdale Street and Olson Place Southwest (SR 509 State Turnback - Kenyon to City limits; R/W 7939).
